==政府組成==
選舉過後，[[庫拉努黨|庫拉努黨]]、[[猶太人家園|猶太人家園]]、[[沙斯党|沙斯党]]、[[以色列是我们的家园|以色列是我们的家园]]和[[聖經猶太教聯盟|聖經猶太教聯盟]]向總統[[鲁文·里夫林|鲁文·里夫林]]提議指派來自[[利库德集团|利库德集团]]的時任總理[[本雅明·内塔尼亚胡|本雅明·内塔尼亚胡]]組織新內閣，而以上各政黨在新一屆國會的120席中合共擁有過半數的67席。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jpost.com/Israel-Elections/Rivlin-continues-consultations-with-party-representatives-to-form-coalition-394780|title=Rivlin to task Netanyahu with forming coalition after PM wins 67 recommendations|author=Greer Fay Cashman, JPost.com Staff|work=The Jerusalem Post|accessdate=2015-10-09|archive-date=2015-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151020172902/http://www.jpost.com/Israel-Elections/Rivlin-continues-consultations-with-party-representatives-to-form-coalition-394780|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年3月25日，總統[[鲁文·里夫林|鲁文·里夫林]]指派內塔尼亞胡籌組新政府。然而內塔尼亞胡直至4月20日仍未能成功組閣，里夫林把限期推遲至5月6日。<ref>Josef Federman, [http://bigstory.ap.org/article/0e79520583914abdb644baf24bdd4357/israeli-leader-gets-2-week-extension-form-coalition Israeli leader gets 2-week extension to form coalition] {{Wayback|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/0e79520583914abdb644baf24bdd4357/israeli-leader-gets-2-week-extension-form-coalition |date=20150518080531 }} Associated Press, 20 April 2015</ref>

[[阿维格多·利伯曼|阿维格多·利伯曼]]在5月6日限期前不久宣佈他的[[以色列是我们的家园|以色列是我们的家园]]不會與利庫德集團組成聯合政府。<ref>Jodi Rudoren, [http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/05/world/middleeast/avigdor-lieberman-israel-foreign-minister.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=second-column-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news -{Israeli Foreign Minister Says He Won’t Join Netanyahu’s New Government}-] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/05/world/middleeast/avigdor-lieberman-israel-foreign-minister.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=second-column-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news |date=20150507094703 }}, New York Times, 4 May 2015.</ref>最後內塔尼亞胡的利庫德集團與[[庫拉努黨|庫拉努黨]]、[[猶太人家園|猶太人家園]]、[[沙斯党|沙斯党]]和[[聖經猶太教聯盟|聖經猶太教聯盟]]組成聯合政府，在國會只有61席的微弱多數。5月14日，國會以61票支持、59票反對通過新內閣的名單。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lis|first1=Jonathan|title=Israel's 34th government sworn in after stormy debate|url=http://www.haaretz.com/news/israel/1.656536|accessdate=3 June 2015|work=Haaretz (online)|date=14 May 2015|archive-date=2015-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819064019/http://www.haaretz.com/news/israel/1.656536|dead-url=no}}</ref>

